{
  "name": "7 — SharePoint API test (discover sites, then list libraries)",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {},
      "id": "sp_run",
      "name": "Run now",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.manualTrigger",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [0, 300]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "method": "GET",
        "url": "https://graph.microsoft.com/v1.0/sites",
        "authentication": "genericCredentialType",
        "genericAuthType": "oAuth2Api",
        "sendQuery": true,
        "queryParameters": {
          "parameters": [
            { "name": "search", "value": "*" },
            { "name": "$select", "value": "id,name,displayName,webUrl" },
            { "name": "$top", "value": "200" }
          ]
        },
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "sp_all",
      "name": "1. All sites the app can see",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
      "typeVersion": 4.2,
      "position": [220, 300],
      "credentials": {
        "oAuth2Api": {
          "id": "ieNwdcRlBlCL0EM0",
          "name": "SharePoint API"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "method": "GET",
        "url": "https://graph.microsoft.com/v1.0/sites/root",
        "authentication": "genericCredentialType",
        "genericAuthType": "oAuth2Api",
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "sp_root",
      "name": "2. Root site (auth sanity check)",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
      "typeVersion": 4.2,
      "position": [440, 300],
      "credentials": {
        "oAuth2Api": {
          "id": "ieNwdcRlBlCL0EM0",
          "name": "SharePoint API"
        }
      },
      "onError": "continueRegularOutput"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "method": "GET",
        "url": "https://graph.microsoft.com/v1.0/sites/PASTE_SITE_ID_HERE/lists",
        "authentication": "genericCredentialType",
        "genericAuthType": "oAuth2Api",
        "sendQuery": true,
        "queryParameters": {
          "parameters": [
            { "name": "$select", "value": "id,name,displayName,webUrl,list" }
          ]
        },
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "sp_lists",
      "name": "3. Lists & libraries (paste a site id first)",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
      "typeVersion": 4.2,
      "position": [660, 300],
      "disabled": true,
      "credentials": {
        "oAuth2Api": {
          "id": "ieNwdcRlBlCL0EM0",
          "name": "SharePoint API"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## How to test (after IT added Sites.Read.All + admin consent)\n1. **Execute workflow.** Node 1 returns every SharePoint site the app can see — `displayName` + `webUrl` per site. Node 2 is just an auth sanity check (root site).\n2. Find the site that holds the **weekly reports** (recognisable from displayName/webUrl). Copy its `id` (the long `tecknuovo.sharepoint.com,guid,guid` string).\n3. Paste that id into node 3's URL (replace PASTE_SITE_ID_HERE), enable the node, run again → you get the document libraries/lists on that site.\n\n**If node 1 returns an empty `value` array or 403:** the permission isn't consented yet, or it was added as *Delegated* instead of **Application** — ask IT to double-check both.",
        "height": 320,
        "width": 480
      },
      "id": "sp_note",
      "name": "How to test",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [0, -80]
    }
  ],
  "connections": {
    "Run now": {
      "main": [[{ "node": "1. All sites the app can see", "type": "main", "index": 0 }]]
    },
    "1. All sites the app can see": {
      "main": [[{ "node": "2. Root site (auth sanity check)", "type": "main", "index": 0 }]]
    },
    "2. Root site (auth sanity check)": {
      "main": [[{ "node": "3. Lists & libraries (paste a site id first)", "type": "main", "index": 0 }]]
    }
  },
  "settings": { "executionOrder": "v1" }
}
